rComments: He was fantastic! Could always go to him for help and he was very passionate about what he talked about! Loved him! Great Prof!

He was pretty average. Hated the group work project. He was SO unclear on expectations. He explained it SO much and still most people misunderstood the actual format of the paper. His textbook is annoying and there's way too much reading. Final exam was BAD. Essay question was way too vague!!!

Great professor! you can really tell he cares about what he does and that his students are doing well and understanding course material! Very easy to talk to and get clarity on questions or feedback from exams and essays. Easy to get a good mark as long as you go to class and do the readings. His class is not boring either, I found it enjoyable

Really good professor. Very clear, straight-forward and doesn't play any games. Pretty much lays out exactly what you need to study, no tricks. Fair marker and funny to listen to as he has a little bit of a French accent. Overall, great class, great prof and fairly easy to obtain marks. I would recommend it!
